title: 12/16: Weekend Recap - Too Many Duds (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
Things didn't play out exactly as we expected, so let's kick off today's show with our Week 15 surprises (2:20). We're talking about two RBs who were surprising studs and the ineptitude in the NE-PIT game. Plus news and notes (8:28) and IdiotMoron moves (12:00) ... How about the MegaDuds (13:40) from Week 15!? The Colts and Cowboys gave us several, and Saquon Barkley and Adam Thielen were dreadful. Then we move on to the Leaderboard at QB (21:50), RB (24:28), WR (29:25) and TE (32:09) ... Recapping every game with our Fantasy thoughts (35:00) ... Email us at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
